longBusinessDescription:
ABzero is a startup that develops innovative medical devices and offers a system of transport of blood, blood products and organs through automatic drones, ensuring delivery in an autonomous and immediate manner and in total safety for the human component, even in case of failure. The transported goods are stored safely in a smart capsule, which protects their quality according to the law. The system is based on an intuitive, proprietary and effective software, easy to use by the medical staff. The core of our technology, the intelligent capsule, is unique.
The hospital operator will just have to put the blood bags into the appropriate temperature-controlled compartment and enter the code of the recipient structure. ABzero will start automatically following the most convenient preset route.
The Drones ABzero, however, have the innovative feature that is not present in any of the drones of competition: they are equipped with a special capsule that can contain delicate and deteriorating substances such as blood, blood and blood components, but also drugs susceptible to temperature variations during transport (eg vaccines).
Their features are unique:
Drone: ABzero does not produce drones, but uses commercial drones that puts the healthcare facility at its disposal, along with proprietary software for use by healthcare professionals and the patented smart capsule for blood, organ or hemomponent transport. This will ensure high safety standards and advanced flight performance;
Smart Capsule: Smart Capsules is the core of our technology, patented, and engages in any type of commercial drone modularly. The smart capsules are designed to achieve maximum strength and minimum weight while complying with the standards required by law such as, for example, maintaining maintenance temperature, hermetic closure, and agitation of the hemocomponents. All modules are interchangeable and guaranteed to last in safety;
Intuitive Owner Software: The system is based on intuitive, proprietary and effective software, easy to use by the medical staff, which in turn uses advanced, commercial, and open source flight control systems;
Flight Times: ABzero drones reduce delivery times over short distances (up to 10 km) and up to 50% over medium distances (up to 40 km) up to 80%;
Load: ABzero drones have a loading capacity of up to 10 kg
Price: ABzero offers a fast and secure delivery service, 24 hours a day and 7 days a week, which results in savings in direct and indirect costs.

